{"tid":1006421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 社協：150都是年青的！醫院「逼爆」源於香港老人","createTime":"2019-02-03T03:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T15:34:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"038e3a5bc7b9e2221fefb6959fd3ccb6128933fe","tid":1006421,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"社會上有意見指，本港每日有150個新移民名額，直接影響本港醫療體制發展。社區組織協會幹事彭鴻昌今日出席商業電台節目《政好星期天》時強調，評論時應按事實基礎。他指出，每年約有兩萬多人確定在港定居，這批人的年齡中位數約30多歲，較本港人口年齡中位數逾40歲為高，<span style=\"color: red;\">新移民當中亦有逾八成是40歲以下，是年青的一群。</span><br />\n<br />\n彭鴻昌續指，人口老化才是令公營醫院「逼爆」的原因，現時55歲以上的人士使用約一半醫療資源，65歲以上病人住院量佔整體住院量的一半，反問「如果要源頭減人，係咪要減走老人家？」重申醫生應視乎病人醫療需要，提供適切服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2400565/org/7baadb262ca0656cb0b47afac94bb4ba.jpg/7p2QHVMfR8ygi3JuRsoovtLtEBov3REAnlWEWZ5VhFk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2400565%2Forg%2F7baadb262ca0656cb0b47afac94bb4ba.jpg%2F7p2QHVMfR8ygi3JuRsoovtLtEBov3REAnlWEWZ5VhFk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7fffdf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/291147/流感高峰-人口老化增醫療負荷-社協-源頭減人要減走老人家\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F291147%2F%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%80%81%E5%8C%96%E5%A2%9E%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E8%B2%A0%E8%8D%B7-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%94-%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E6%B8%9B%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B8%9B%E8%B5%B0%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7sjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=1788e3cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/291147/流感高峰-人口老化增醫療負荷-社協-源頭減人要減走老人家</a>"},{"pid":"eee30c3cef40f238df17e11512c263878ce35d29","tid":1006421,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:38:29.000Z","msg":"40歲仲年青？"},{"pid":"4bccb56df0cf3956210a2be5c0045cfe19947610","tid":1006421,"uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0