-size: xx-large;\">只講百分比, 唔講實際數字</span></strong></span><br />\n佢2016年已係1020個65歲以上, <br />\n20年黎, 就係輸入20000個<br />\n新増2萬個65歲以上新移蝗, 唔迫爆病床就有鬼啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/7zqYuK0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zqYuK0.png&h=b7f14d08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdc3d7672f89eab3a686e8e85dc84a6231be5056","tid":1006421,"uid":82291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"朋友做醫院<br />\n腫瘤科<br />\n好多4-50新移民拿左身份證係大陸做野<br />\n有事返香港醫，<br />\n老婆仔女等新移民就住深圳讀上水的學校<br />\n之後差不多死，就成家拿綜援"},{"pid":"837a88f9e9d3c03ce551caa233859318b3d75abd","tid":1006421,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a101414a605203ebb1b6ddef2f0079b8147dd4d","tid":1006421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"d2bf941ea007ef67c8a8714bcdc9d8a8cffaf56d","tid":1006421,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc3d7672f89eab3a686e8e85dc84a6231be5056","tid":1006421,"uid":82291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"朋友做醫院<br />\n腫瘤科<br />\n好多4-50新移民拿左身份證係大陸做野<br />\n有事返香港醫，<br />\n老婆仔女等新移民就住深圳讀上水的學校<br />\n之後差不多死，就成家拿綜援"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"收埋D錢係支那, 係支那有幾層樓<br />\n<br />\n黎香港就隱瞞資產搶公屋"},{"pid":"0f6cf351871b41fef5f6d302e4ebb01eec09618b","tid":1006421,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"呢班新香港人，咳幾聲就話想留院，個仔輪急症無得打尖就打護士 (打一個少一個，排隊時間更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"a17c02b2d5a864b7291fc31df785fcb8043943f2","tid":1006421,"uid":242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:29:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾議員保護每日150條蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下屆邊個話取消150條蟲邊個可以做議員！一定夠票做議員"},{"pid":"0cfc77a8b9776169949bc52c05a1bf077f65c2ae","tid":1006421,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"其實都唔明你班港豬嬲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂開心又一日唔開心又一日<br />\n點解要理埋煩埋呢啲無謂嘢搞到自己唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正你都改變唔到啲乜㗎啦<br />\n每日150?<br />\n班人落到嚟排公屋住劏房啫<br />\n又唔係住喺我隔籬<br />\n況且公屋我都冇份排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫院迫爆?<br />\n公司醫療加自己出面搭多份醫保<br />\n大小病都係去私家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺有乜影響<br />\n納稅人啲錢同政府資源俾晒佢哋?<br />\n反正自己揾夠自己食<br />\n本身正常人都唔會諗靠政府㗎啦<br />\n況且香港稅率不嬲低冇期望有乜回報<br />\n同埋講真你去邊個國家住都係要交稅㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n其實唔關自己事嘅理咁多做乜?<br />\n知完理完嬲完喇，生活會好咗咩?<br />\n做人要識分吓輕重<br />\n有時間都諗吓點樣投資吓揾多個錢快手供甩層樓好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放假得閒都plan吓幾時去日本韓國玩散吓心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁做人唔係輕鬆好多咩?<br />\n呢啲無聊嘢關人柒事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d901334ceffee84f8c3537086c51614142fd78d","tid":1006421,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cfc77a8b9776169949bc52c05a1bf077f65c2ae","tid":1006421,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"其實都唔明你班港豬嬲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂開心又一日唔開心又一日<br />\n點解要理埋煩埋呢啲無謂嘢搞到自己唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正你都改變唔到啲乜㗎啦<br />\n每日150?<br />\n班人落到嚟排公屋住劏房啫<br />\n又唔係住喺